summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground easements over portions of Burke's 2nd Addition to the City of Seattle; Government Lot 10 in Section 4, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; Wallis' Country Club Tracts; vacated Gilman Avenue West; Kittinger's Addition to the City of Seattle; vacated Yale Avenue North; Charlston Addition; and the southeast quarter of Section 26, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, as described below and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
